The State moves to delete the repeater enhancer.  Motion granted.
NO CONTEST plea entered to the charge of maintain drug trafficking place.  Convicted.
Sentence Withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for two (2) years.
Conditions of probation:
1) Spend sixty (60) days in the county jail, under the Huber Law, commencing on 08-27-15 at 6:00 p.m.;
2) AODA assessment and follow through;
3) Submit to random urine screens and pay for same;
4) Maintain absolute sobriety;
5) Maintain fulltime employment/schooling/combination;
6) Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Departments assessment process;
7) Pay court costs;
8) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
9) provide DNA sample and pay the surcharge.
Minutes.
